  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Tasmanian Tiger SK 插板胸挂（黑系复合迷彩）",
      "en": "Tasmanian Tiger SK plate carrier (MultiCam Black)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "TT SK",
      "en": "TT SK"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 39,347₽ | 物品价值: 127,148 | Ragman报价: 78,832₽容器效率: x0.89 (8/9)\n\n购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 272,000₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 猫雕 x2 | Σ ≈ 77,974₽\n\nTT SK插板胸挂选用轻薄、耐用的层压TPU Cordura尼龙材料，面料密度高达700旦。这款胸挂带有两个插板、可调节的肩带和腰带。附带能够收纳四个弹匣的口袋。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 39,347₽ | 物品价值: 127,148 | Ragman报价: 78,832₽容器效率: x0.89 (8/9)\n\n购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 272,000₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级3 < 猫雕 x2 | Σ ≈ 77,974₽\n\nThe ultra-light and skeletal TT Plate Carrier SK vest is made primarily from lightweight, thin and durable TPU-laminated Cordura nylon material with a claimed density of at least 700 denier. The design of the vest provides two lightweight covers for plates, adjustable shoulder straps and a light waist jumper. Equipped with a front panel for 4 magazines."
    },
